title: Starland Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A typical lunch menu comprise soups, salads, and sandwiches. The kitchen uses some herbs grown in the rear of the restaurant. Servers are knowledegable about vegan options. Some items can be made vegan by request. Order at the counter. The cafe is on the lower floor of an old house with seating on the porch and in the back.
